column1: - d BENEF := d(VBNP-(IT + ITCEE) + SUB-DPUU-(WCF + SSFFIC + WDOM + WBG + YN) -(GOSH-DPUH + IDH) -DTF-RIDGG + YIDG)

- dln (DTH/(NATY-UY) ) := 1.4 * dln(((WBU_ + YN + GOSH_) -(SSF + SSH) ) /(PC*(NATY-UY) ) ) + dln PC + ((DTHX*40.34) /DTH[-1 ]) -(20/DTH[-1 ]) *(TIME= 2001) -(30/DTH[-1 ]) *(TIME= 2005) -(30/DTH[-1 ]) *(TIME= 2006)
- ITD := (ITDR/(1 + ITDR) ) *(VC + QOUG + VIF + IUG + VI5 + VS)
- ITT := EXC + ITPL + ITD + ITPR + ITPS
- ln (KLFHP/KLFHPO) := ln (KLFHP/KLFHPO) [-1 ] + 0.0065 + -0.0606*(ln (KLFHP/KLFHPO) -ln PKF + ln WCRH) [-1 ] + -0.0578*d(-ln PKF + ln WCRH)
- dln KNFF := -0.9774 + 0.1413*ln(QAFF_/(Q_F + Q_I) ) [-1 ] + 0.0335*ln mavg(3, (VAFF_-WCF_-WIND_-DTF) /(PIF*KNFF[-1 ]* (RLBER + VKFF + 0.1000) ) ) + KNFFO + 0.4156*mavg(4, dln QAFF_)
- PFI := ((PC*(1-ITCR) *QC) + (PQOG*(1-ITGR) *QGO) + (PIF*(1-ITIFR) * QIF) + (PIG*(1-ITIGR) *QIG) + (PI5*(1-ITI5R) *QI5) + VS) /(QC + QGO + QI + QS)
- r PFND := r((VC + CGU + VI + VS) /(QC + QG + QI + QS) )

- dln((PIF/PIFO) *(1-ITIFR) ) := (0.5689*d(.8*dln AOUC + .2*dln PMAB) + 0.3287*((.8*dln AOUC + .2*dln PMAB) -dln((PIF/PIFO) *(1-ITIFR) ) ) [-1 ] + dln ((PIF/PIFO) *(1-ITIFR) ) [-1 ]) *0 + dln PC/(1 + ITCR)
- grt PWBG := .5*((grt TWG) *(WBGP/WBG) [-1 ] + (grt TWGP) *(YSFIC/WBG) [-1 ]) + grt ZJ
- r QBBP := r(QC + QG + QI + QS + (QX-QM) )
- r QBBPPOT_ := r(Q_F + Q_I + QAGHP + QAHHP + ITNQHP) *(TIME<1999) + r(Q_F + Q_I + QAG + QAH + ITNQ) *(TIME>1998)
- r QBBP_B := r(QC + QG + QI + QS + (QX-QM) )
- r QFND := r(QC + QG + QI + QS)
- r QM := r (QMAB + QME + QMS + QMT)
- r QX := r(QXAB + QXE + QXS + QXT)
- SF := GOSF + YSSF + OCUF-(DTF + SBF + IDF + VAMARE)
- SG := GOSG + IT + YDTG + YSSG + COTRES + OCUG-CGU-IDG-SUB + SUBCEE-SBG
- SSH := YSEFT1 + YSEFT2 + SSH3WW + SSH3WA + SSH3ZA + SSH3ZW
- r WLCP := r ZJ * r ULCP
- grt YDH_ := grt((WBU_ + YN + GOSH_ + IDH) -(SSF + SSH + DTH) + (SBH + OCUH) )
- grt ZF := grt PC + ZX-0.05*grt PME
- grt ZJ := grt PC + ZX-0.05*grt PME
